                  on July 23. TheWeekly Northwestern Gazettehad also published areportof the speech on July 29. The original speech in Lincoln’s hand has not been located;
                  however, a fragment of aspeechon the topic of sectionalism in Lincoln’s hand is extant.Weekly Northwestern Gazette(Galena, IL), 29 July 1856, 2:5.

